ProMED-mail
e-mail: promed@usa.healthnet.org
[This apparent cluster of cases of invasive streptococcal disease has been
reported for a period of weeks, but as yet no microbiological
characterization of strains isolated has been available. It is clear that
there is a problem at this facility, but until the strain analyses are
performed it will not be clear whether they are dealing with a common
source outbreak or a breakdown in good medical/nursing practices. - Mod.ES
